title: Kahin Pyar Na Ho Jaye
subTitle: Prem's heart fills with despair when the woman he loves fails to show up for their wedding day. However, his life soon takes an unexpected turn with the arrival of a new neighbour.

title: Hera Pheri
subTitle: Vijay and Ajay make a living by stealing money from people. Their friendship is affected when Vijay discovers that Ajay's father may have been his father's killer.

title: Bhoothnath Returns
subTitle: After returning to Earth to scare children, the ghost Bhoothnath befriends Akhrot and helps him earn money. Unexpectedly, they take on the country's most powerful politician.

title: Student of the Year 2
subTitle: Rohan follows his lover, Mridula, to St Teresa's college hoping to reunite with her. There, he befriends Manav, the most popular student, but is constantly at loggerheads with his sister, Shreya.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: Thakur marries his mistress when his first wife, Pooja, is unable to bear children. His brother-in-law opposes this marriage to save the dignity of his sister and fights to reunite them.

title: Rakshak
subTitle: ASP Raj Sinha is assigned to catch the criminal responsible for printing and circulating fake currency notes. However, he is shocked to learn that the person is none other than his childhood friend.

title: Dil Pardesi Ho Gayaa
subTitle: When Major Ram of the Indian Army is captured by the Pakistani military, his younger brother Sunny begins a daring mission to rescue him, only to find himself falling for a Pakistani woman.

title: Border
subTitle: A small battalion of Indian soldiers go up against a 2000 well-armed Pakistani strike force. They must defend their post all night until they receive assistance from the Indian Air Force.

title: Farishtay
subTitle: Veeru and Dheeru live under the tyrant ruler, Raja Jaichand. Later, they embark on a mission and strive to overcome challenges to defeat the dictator.

title: Naagin Bani Suhaagan
subTitle: Vaishali, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, is blessed with a boon to transform herself into a shapeshifting snake. She falls into a dilemma when circumstances force her to go against her love.

title: Bol Bachchan
subTitle: A man constructs increasingly intricate lies about his identity to prevent getting into trouble for breaking into a Hindu temple.

title: Chhota Bheem and the Curse of Damyaan
subTitle: Bheem and his loyal group of friends embark on a dangerous mission to defeat the evil demon Damyaan and save the world from his villainous plans.

subTitle: Maa Beti

title: Taarzan: The Wonder Car
subTitle: Raj revamps his deceased father's car into a wonderful car named Taarzan and the car comes alive as it is possessed by his father's spirit. Soon, it also starts killing his father's murderers.

title: Sainik
subTitle: When Lieutenant Suraj goes missing, his father believes he is dead and decides to keep the news from his daughter and his son's wife. However, they already know and choose to put up a brave front.

title: Ishq
subTitle: Ranjit and Harbanslal, two rich businessmen, hatch a malicious plan when they discover that their children have fallen in love with individuals from the poorer sections of society.

title: Ghulam-E-Musthafa
subTitle: A notorious hitman forsakes a life of crime after his lady love suffers a tragic death due to his professional rivalries. However, the mafia compels him to return for a final hit job.

title: Aladin
subTitle: Aladin, an orphan tormented by bullies, discovers a magic lamp that grants him incredible powers. Later, with the help of a genie, he embarks on thrilling adventures to defeat the evil Ringmaster.

title: Bal Hanuman 4: Attack of the Universe
subTitle: When Chote Maharaj arranges an intense kabaddi tournament between monkeys and crocodiles, the treacherous reptiles conspire to resurrect their demon king using support from extraterrestrial allies.

title: Angrezi Medium
subTitle: A Rajasthani father goes to extreme lengths to help a daughter pursue higher studies in London. Along the way, misadventures and misunderstandings put their relationship through its paces.

title: Charanon Ki Saugandh
subTitle: After returning to his village, Ravi learns that the local farmers are being oppressed by a despotic landlord. Soon, he decides to contest the panchayat elections against the tyrant and put an end to his cruel rule.

title: Bal Ganesh
subTitle: Bal Ganesh, the mischievous son of Lord Shiva, embarks on several adventures with Mooshak the mouse, his friend and vehicle. Despite being young, he battles evil forces and protects the world.

title: Ab Ke Baras
subTitle: Anjali comes to India to investigate recurring visions of her past life in her dreams. Later, she meets a thief who might have been her lover in another lifetime.

title: Banjaran
subTitle: The universe offers a Banjara tribe leader's daughter an opportunity to turn her doomed love story into a happily-ever-after with her soulmate.

title: Kabhi Khushi Kabhie Gham ...
subTitle: Rahul, the adopted older son of a rich couple, is banished by his father when he chooses to marry a middle-class woman. Years later, his younger brother, Rohan, sets out to find him.

title: Benaam Badsha
subTitle: An abandoned child shaped by violence grows into a feared criminal until a brave woman attempts to transform his brutal path through empathy and unwavering resolve.
